KESHTGAR
v.
U.S. BANK. No. S220012. Supreme Court of California April 27, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, CUÉLLAR, and KRUGER, JJ., concur.

The above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division Six, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of Yvanova v. New Century Mortgage Corp. (2016) 62 Cal.4th 919 , 199 Cal.Rptr.3d 66 , 365 P.3d 845 . (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
